This project has following file structure:

├── bill.rb
├── product.rb
├── user.rb
└── spec
    ├── bill_spec.rb
    ├── product_spec.rb
    ├── user_spec.rb
    ├── README
    ├── spec_helper.rb
    └── support
        └── matchers
            └── be_same_number_as.rb



Files bill.rb, product.rb and user.rb are main class files of the code.

Directory spec contains test cases for the classes defined, using rspec and additional match helpers for rspec.

To run the test cases:

> rspec spec

This code has been tested in Ruby version 1.9.2 and Rspec gem version 2.8.0
